41
00:05:27,490 --> 00:05:30,220
SPEAKER_17: Master Fugui is going home. You take him.

140
00:14:44,779 --> 00:14:47,769
SPEAKER_17: I am very sorry, but you've got nothing left.

141
00:14:48,049 --> 00:14:51,779
SPEAKER_17: What could you stake the bet on?
We don't accept empty bets.

163
00:17:30,210 --> 00:17:32,400
SPEAKER_17: Mr. Xu, any mistakes?

289
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:45,220
SPEAKER_17: The wounded who froze to death.

301
00:33:58,930 --> 00:34:00,589
SPEAKER_17: They've all run off.

302
00:34:00,660 --> 00:34:02,130
SPEAKER_17: How could that be?

313
00:34:31,230 --> 00:34:32,460
SPEAKER_17: So, no running?

778
01:27:58,970 --> 01:28:00,869
SPEAKER_17: Comrade Wan Erxi.

814
01:31:08,659 --> 01:31:10,680
SPEAKER_17: I brought some colleagues.

815
01:31:10,760 --> 01:31:12,779
SPEAKER_17: We're fixing the place up.

818
01:31:18,529 --> 01:31:21,369
SPEAKER_17: And we've painted Chairman Mao's portrait.

822
01:31:36,520 --> 01:31:38,449
SPEAKER_17: We must be going.

829
01:32:01,979 --> 01:32:04,810
SPEAKER_17: Thanks, we'll go to the factory bathhouse.

863
01:36:16,430 --> 01:36:17,989
SPEAKER_17: Chairman Mao...

864
01:36:18,869 --> 01:36:21,600
SPEAKER_17: Comrade Fengxia's mine now.

897
01:40:04,689 --> 01:40:06,279
SPEAKER_17: Dad! Mom!

913
01:41:23,939 --> 01:41:28,000
SPEAKER_17: I just came from the hospital.
The doctor says it's due in autumn.

934
01:42:41,649 --> 01:42:43,579
SPEAKER_17: I had the photo framed.

945
01:43:29,000 --> 01:43:31,829
SPEAKER_17: They held a public trial against him.

1042
01:50:52,210 --> 01:50:54,829
SPEAKER_17: Do as Mommy says and push.

1043
01:50:54,909 --> 01:50:56,640
SPEAKER_17: Everything will be fine.

1074
01:53:13,180 --> 01:53:14,939
SPEAKER_17: Wang Bin! Stand up!

1075
01:53:19,020 --> 01:53:22,050
SPEAKER_17: This is the same Wang Bin
who once insulted...

1076
01:53:22,460 --> 01:53:26,359
SPEAKER_17: me and my wife,
saying she wasn't fit to reproduce.

1078
01:53:31,029 --> 01:53:33,159
SPEAKER_17: We dragged him here today...

1079
01:53:33,300 --> 01:53:36,270
SPEAKER_17: to educate him, to criticize him...

1080
01:53:37,340 --> 01:53:39,899
SPEAKER_17: and to let him witness her giving birth.

1081
01:53:39,970 --> 01:53:42,909
SPEAKER_17: To show him the heirs
of this new, Red world.

1086
01:54:03,300 --> 01:54:05,289
SPEAKER_17: That's professor Wang...

1087
01:54:05,500 --> 01:54:07,229
SPEAKER_17: head of obstetrics.

1088
01:54:15,010 --> 01:54:17,029
SPEAKER_17: Dr. Wang, don't be afraid.

1089
01:54:17,439 --> 01:54:19,439
SPEAKER_17: I was putting on a show.

1090
01:54:20,180 --> 01:54:21,699
SPEAKER_17: We're not accusing you.

1091
01:54:21,779 --> 01:54:23,770
SPEAKER_17: My wife's having a baby.

1157
01:59:32,659 --> 01:59:35,289
SPEAKER_17: - How is he?
- They're both fine!

1158
01:59:35,359 --> 01:59:37,689
SPEAKER_17: Erxi, you're a lucky man!

1171
02:00:25,310 --> 02:00:28,539
SPEAKER_17: You two get the car, we'll be fine.

1172
02:00:40,989 --> 02:00:42,590
SPEAKER_17: Have some water.

1253
02:07:11,979 --> 02:07:13,350
SPEAKER_17: It's okay.

1262
02:07:42,550 --> 02:07:44,180
SPEAKER_17: Not just buns...

1263
02:07:44,279 --> 02:07:46,310
SPEAKER_17: anything made from wheat.

